Package lab4

Class Coach

java.lang.Object
lab4.Coach
class Coach extends Object
This class represent the coach that trains the team's players. A coach has a name, a number of years of experience, and a level of expertise. The level of expertise can be represented by one of the strings: "high", "average", or "beginner".
